'''Coolsap trees''' were densely-leaved [[Tree/Legends|trees]] that were native to the [[Planet/Legends|world]] of [[Gamorr/Legends|Gamorr]], the [[Homeworld/Legends|homeworld]] of the [[Gamorrean/Legends|Gamorrean]] [[Species/Legends|species]]. Their name came from the fact that their sap was icy cold as was used as coolant in some ships.

